{
  "stem": "12447.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I walked in-- I seen a parish priest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I walked into the priest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I spoke to him, and I told him who I am and everything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I explained him that I have a disease.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not as a Jew, but I explained that I'm a Polack, and all that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm Polish kid, and my father, and all this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This never changed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This story stuck with me all the way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he says to me-- I told him that I would probably be able to hire out, to get myself work and everything if I can only get through with this disease.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I cannot get rid of this disease.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, I had, prior to that, some-- what I-- it's detail that I-- a Polack took me in once.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he tried to get me some medication.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, he pulled my pants off and saw that I was a Jew and tried to sell me out or whatever.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, I got to this priest, and I told him this story.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he said, I'll tell you, there is, within maybe 10 kilometers, a hospital that-- you go over there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there is a very rich man that is-- he owns a lot of land.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He's a landowner over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He's one of these noblemen, a Polack, and you tell him this story.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Tell him that I send you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The only thing-- he's going to have a problem getting into the hospital because the hospital is run by Germans, and all that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I had no choice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I figured, if I continue like that, I'm-- I was falling apart already.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I got myself to this nobleman, I told him the story, and he said, let me see what I can do for you.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
